title: Worst Date Wednesday: Things Just Got So Awkward
description: Leslie joins us for her story on Worst Date Wednesday. A guy she matched with on Tinder went on a date to Perkins. He got political during their first date, did things you shouldn't do on a date, and talked about some very boring things that she had no interest in talking about.
